          "Authors create a predictive model that is meant to predict how many years the student took finish the program.\n\nThis prediction is particularly trivial since it uses data from the entire program.\n\nOne approach that distinguishes this work from others though is that it clusters first and then predicts.\n\nThere is benchmarking of general model vs cluster-specific model",
